author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
Join the Glass Cannon Network, and spider-editor extraordinaire Nick Lowe, as they explore another wacky corner of the Marvel Multiverse. 

In this amazing Spider-Verse improv special, narrator Troy Lavallee returns with Skid Maher, Joe O’Brien, Matthew Capodicasa, Sydney Amanuel, and Marvel's Nick Lowe for a spectacular and unexpected journey through the Marvel Universe. Heroes have been disappearing across the multiverse, and it’s up to Spider-Man Noir and team to find out who’s behind it.

Interested in creating your own adventures? Learn more about the Marvel Multiverse Role-Playing Game: https://marvel.com/rpg

The Marvel Multiverse Role-Playing Game is available now wherever books are sold:

Amazon: https://www.amazon.com/MARVEL-MULTIVERSE-ROLE-PLAYING-GAME-RULEBOOK/dp/1302927833

Roll20: https://pages.roll20.net/marvel-multiverse

Demiplane: https://app.demiplane.com/nexus/marvelrpg

Barnes & Noble: https://www.barnesandnoble.com/w/marvel-multiverse-role-playing-game-matt-forbe
title: Spider-Noir Solves a Multiversal Whodunnit! | Marvel Multiverse RPG
